commit_list.message: Add names to tags in uploadPage
Implement function that calls request-proccessor according to e-poll
Set last two variables for cgi runner
Fix log service, new logs are append at the end of log-file
Implement default page case, free some memory when needed
Implement handling of case when whost, document and cgi dirs aren't provided
Make some logic changes in cache-control feature
Add starting file, the main method
Fix bugs with inodes marked as 'removed'
Implement relative to absolute path conversion
Comment swap functions and delete commented code
Comment VM utility functions in C file
Adjust code to the changed interface
Add offset and overshoot to page mapping(for loading ELF segments)
Make sure, a program larger than RAM can be loaded, if swap is implemented
Fix compile errors and a file mapping bug.
Add initialisation and cleanup of mapped files
Add code to load so that load status functions as intended
Add load status and load lock to thre thread
Implement wait and exit system calls
Define, how the child system works.
Add a way for the thread to remember it's name and the file of the application
Temporarily revert back thre changes to the thread

Add process wait with proper synchronization

Process wait was added and necessary synchronization
in thread.h thread.c and process.c

Add child_lock

For avoiding concurrency problems,
locks were added here

Add child_thread struct

Child thread that will be used by parents
to check for correct pid while waiting added

Add Design Document

A desing document that answers
many questions and explains
how our project works.

Fix thread creation yielding

While creating thread, if the new thread's
priority is lower than this one's, yield
happens, as requested in task.

Begin implementation of mlfq scheduler

The multi level feedback scheduler
helper functions to update load
average every multiple of a second
and calculate thread priority

Implement next_thread_to_run

Implements next thread by returning
maximum priority thread.

Roll back temporarily some changes

Since we have more errors than passes,
rewriting may be the only option
Add readme.txt to not be ignored

Add bash like printing and fix getter

The getter, which was supposed to print
scaled results according to flags,
now does exactly that, so this is
a fix.

Fix ulimit limits

Changed divisors and refactored code
to make the syscalls right
Add constants.h and fix flag bug in ulimit

Add echo last status code function

Implemented with static variable,
this function will be available for
everyone to use and update the last
status code.

Fix warnings and simple errors because of includes

Added all necessary includes so that no warnings
or errors are generated because of them

Replaces functions, so that they're seperate

ulimit, nice are in different header/.c files
now

Add half version of nice and change prototypes

nice without given argument is written
and prototypes were changed according to
needs.

Add ulimit work for both setting and getting

ulimit function now avoids code repetition and
we added correct behaviour for -S -H. Getting
and setting is now passed via function pointer

Add ulimit function with most flags

only some flags are ommited like -p which doesn't have
a corresponding C RLIMIT resource constant

Add util files to store utility functions

Util.h and util.c will store helper functions,
like an error message display one that's already
added in this commit.
Add ignoring of ctrl+c and ctrl+z
Add gitignore to include only .c .h .gitignore and makefile
